{
  "stem": "20035.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are you a twin?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No other word, absolutely none.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's strictly the finger, the thumb.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was just a tall, very good-looking very, very good-looking, tall German officer, who-- we knew it from the uniform-- that he was-- he was a-- a medic.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in the medical profession.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But just that-- how do you call it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A stone-faced nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, we were marched into-- my brother and I are holding onto each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We thought, at that time, that here is the famous separation where dad and grandpa are not going to be able to work as hard as him and me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In our mind, that's what's happening right now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the reason why we were separated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That the older people, all the middle-aged and older people went one way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went the other way, to the harder labor camp, or whatever they were able to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were ushered into a-- little barracks, little rooms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were not bigger than, I don't know, 30 by 30 feet, 30 feet by 30 feet.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So let's say 1,000 square feet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, the instruction was get undressed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because you are going to be disinfected, cleaned and disinfected.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Keep your clothes in a nice pile, and onto the next room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we get undressed, onto the next room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the next room, all human hair was removed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't have to-- you understand, that anywhere where human hair grows, with a shear it was removed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hair from underarm, hair over the head, and like I said, wherever hair grows.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then onto the next room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next room, they asked the question that-- which I found that-- I mean, I was, once again, just too young to understand what's happening.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
